					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">FCEUX has been set to New PPU the whole time. The status bar is still rock solid in that one.<br /><br />I put in a loop to delay the scroll write until Nintendulator was reporting it happening at a tick somewhere in the low 300s (305 to about 311; it varies a bit). It was still jittery. Is that during hblank? I wasn't quite sure from the link, but I got the impression that it's basically any time after tick 257?<br /><br />To clarify a little, the status bar is solid when the screen isn't moving. If you just sit there, it looks solid. When the screen scrolls though, sometimes the status bar almost &quot;jumps to catch up&quot; as it were (but sometimes it doesn't and looks fine). I attached the rom in case you want to see the effect.</div>

					
